<h3 style="color: red;"><a href="http://iitk.vlab.co.in/index.php?sub=27&amp;brch=236&amp;sim=1275&amp;cnt=2598"><u><span class="CLS_Headin"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><em>Before performing the experiments, make sure that you have gone through all the steps given in the section</em></span></span><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><em> <big>&#39;Few important things to DO befor going to the experiments&#39; </big>and installed all the essential softwares mandatory for running the experiments. If you&#39;ve not done it, click here and go back to that section.</em></span></u></a></h3>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<h3 style="color: red;">&nbsp;</h3>

<h3 style="color: red;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span lang="en-US" style="font-style: italic; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;">Before performing the experimant, you have to download the program. The procedure to download the program is given in detail below:</span></span></h3>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -36pt; margin-left: 36pt;"><span style="unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; direction: ltr; color: black; font-size: 10pt;">&middot;</span><span style="width: 31.5pt;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt;">To download the programs, right click on the link&nbsp;&#39;Simple Harmonic Motion.exe&#39; just below&nbsp;and choose &lsquo;save target as&rsquo;, or, &lsquo;save link as&#39;&nbsp;depending on the browser. </span></strong></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -36pt; margin-left: 36pt;"><strong><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></p>

<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B_4NFirzGX3_SHp0ZmVVT0hRcTA/view?usp=sharing" target="_blank"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font size="5">Simple Harmonic Motion.exe</font></span> </a></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -36pt; margin-left: 36pt;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -36pt; margin-left: 36pt;"><span style="unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; direction: ltr; color: black; font-size: 10pt;">&middot;</span><strong><span style="width: 31.5pt;">&nbsp;</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt;">Save the &lsquo;.zip&rsquo; file to any directory on your PC.</span></strong></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -36pt; margin-left: 36pt;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -36pt; margin-left: 36pt;"><span style="unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; direction: ltr; color: black; font-size: 10pt;">&middot;</span><span style="width: 31.5pt;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt;">Extract the </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;">ALL </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt;">contents of the &lsquo;.zip&rsquo; file to the </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;">SAME </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt;">folder.</span></strong></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -36pt; margin-left: 36pt;"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -36pt; margin-left: 36pt;"><strong><span style="unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; direction: ltr; color: black; font-size: 10pt;">&middot;</span><span style="width: 31.5pt;">&nbsp;</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt;">Double click on the file &ldquo;SHM.exe&rdquo; to start executing the program.</span></strong></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -36pt; margin-left: 36pt;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -36pt; margin-left: 36pt;"><span style="unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; direction: ltr; color: black; font-size: 10pt;">&middot;</span><span style="width: 31.5pt;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt;">Now, perform the experiment as instructed in the video demonstration</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"> provided in the link below:</span></strong></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -36pt; margin-left: 36pt;"><strong><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -36pt; margin-left: 36pt;"><strong><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -36pt; margin-left: 36pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B_4NFirzGX3_OERKTExrUHZLaEU/view?usp=sharing" target="_blank"><strong><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2">Click and download the video instruction for performing the experiment</font></span></strong></a></p>

